    "description": "帮助业余旅行博主凯特·罗宾逊（Kate Robinson）和她的女儿妮可（Nicole）在他们首次巴黎之旅中拯救一座风景如画的酒店，这是一场隐藏物品的冒险游戏，<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第一次来巴黎！</h2> 恢复 Hôtel Hospitalité 的生机，在发现城市隐藏的宝藏和风景如画的街道时，置身于充满活力的巴黎环境中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/3054d2eec492935afe79780bd16326ad.poster.avif?t=1729486956\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/3054d2eec492935afe79780bd16326ad.webm?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/3054d2eec492935afe79780bd16326ad.mp4?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过与法国当地人互动并拥抱这座城市独特的文化，体验爱情之城的真正精髓。通过30多个独特的小游戏，包括在舒适的咖啡馆解开谜题和在繁忙的市场中寻找宝藏，总有新的巴黎冒险等待着你。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/1e784e7b4d91a191214315bdaa62ff27.poster.avif?t=1729486956\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/1e784e7b4d91a191214315bdaa62ff27.webm?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/1e784e7b4d91a191214315bdaa62ff27.mp4?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>探索令人惊叹的巴黎场景<br></li><li>帮助凯特拯救 Hôtel Hospitalité<br></li><li>享受30多个受巴黎启发的迷人小游戏<br></li><li>在无限模式中重访地点<br></li><li>在游戏过程中解锁成就<br></li><li>下载独家壁纸和完整的原声带</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/c218da3455df0dcb11aa2c5fd59f5f7e.poster.avif?t=1729486956\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/c218da3455df0dcb11aa2c5fd59f5f7e.webm?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/c218da3455df0dcb11aa2c5fd59f5f7e.mp4?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>加入凯特和妮可，发现巴黎的心脏和灵魂！<br>Bienvenue à la Ville de l'Amour!",
